title: Free Agency week 1 winners & losers
itunes:title: Free Agency week 1 winners & losers
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler break down the latest news from the NFL, including the Colin Kaepernick saga and the Browns releasing Johnny Manziel. Then, the heroes end the show sharing their winners and losers from the first week of free agency.
